<p>They wanted to ensure the website was accessible by at least 90% of internet-enabled devices, so in making it responsive, it fulfilled that requirement. After the designing process was completed by <a href="http://www.stevenwhitfield.info" target="_blank">Steven Whitfield</a>, a graphic designer from Blitz, I went ahead and developed the final product. The website makes use of CSS3 elements, media queries, HTML5 videos, and HTML5 elements.</p>
